#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.101"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.101:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.101:0.2"
msgid "10. Loṇakapallavagga"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.101:0.3"
msgid "101. Paṃsudhovakasutta"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.254"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: paṃsuvālukā → paṃsuvālikā (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an3.101:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Santi, bhikkhave, jātarūpassa oḷārikā upakkilesā paṃsuvālukā "
"sakkharakaṭhalā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.101:1.2"
msgid ""
"Tamenaṃ paṃsudhovako vā paṃsudhovakantevāsī vā doṇiyaṃ ākiritvā dhovati "
"sandhovati niddhovati."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: thūlavālukā → thūlavālikā (bj, pts1) | thullavālikā (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "an3.101:1.3"
msgid ""
"Tasmiṃ pahīne tasmiṃ byantīkate santi jātarūpassa majjhimasahagatā "
"upakkilesā sukhumasakkharā thūlavālukā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.101:1.4"
msgid ""
"Tamenaṃ paṃsudhovako vā paṃsudhovakantevāsī vā dhovati sandhovati niddhovati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.101:1.5"
msgid ""
"Tasmiṃ pahīne tasmiṃ byantīkate santi jātarūpassa sukhumasahagatā upakkilesā "
"sukhumavālukā kāḷajallikā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.101:1.6"
msgid ""
"Tamenaṃ paṃsudhovako vā paṃsudhovakantevāsī vā dhovati sandhovati niddhovati."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: suvaṇṇasikatāvasissanti → suvaṇṇajātarūpakāvasissanti (mr)
msgctxt "an3.101:1.7"
msgid "Tasmiṃ pahīne tasmiṃ byantīkate athāparaṃ suvaṇṇasikatāvasissanti."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: mūsāyaṃ → musāya (bj)
msgctxt "an3.101:1.8"
msgid ""
"Tamenaṃ suvaṇṇakāro vā suvaṇṇakārantevāsī vā jātarūpaṃ mūsāyaṃ pakkhipitvā "
"dhamati sandhamati niddhamati."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: dhantaṃ sandhantaṃ → adhantaṃ asandhantaṃ (s1-3, km)
#. VAR: niddhantaṃ aniddhantakasāvaṃ → anihitaṃ anikkhittakasāvaṃ (bj) | aniddhantaṃ anihitaṃ aninnītakasāvaṃ (s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an3.101:1.9"
msgid ""
"Taṃ hoti jātarūpaṃ dhantaṃ sandhantaṃ niddhantaṃ aniddhantakasāvaṃ, na ceva "
"mudu hoti na ca kammaniyaṃ, na ca pabhassaraṃ pabhaṅgu ca, na ca sammā upeti "
"kammāya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.101:1.10"
msgid ""
"Hoti so, bhikkhave, samayo yaṃ suvaṇṇakāro vā suvaṇṇakārantevāsī vā taṃ "
"jātarūpaṃ dhamati sandhamati niddhamati."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: niddhantaṃ niddhantakasāvaṃ → nihitaṃ nikkhittakasāvaṃ (bj) | nihitaṃ ninnītakasāvaṃ (s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an3.101:1.11"
msgid ""
"Taṃ hoti jātarūpaṃ dhantaṃ sandhantaṃ niddhantaṃ niddhantakasāvaṃ, mudu ca "
"hoti kammaniyañca pabhassarañca, na ca pabhaṅgu, sammā upeti kammāya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.101:1.12"
msgid ""
"Yassā yassā ca pilandhanavikatiyā ākaṅkhati—yadi paṭṭikāya, yadi kuṇḍalāya, "
"yadi gīveyyake, yadi suvaṇṇamālāya—tañcassa atthaṃ anubhoti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.255"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an3.101:2.1"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, santi adhicittamanuyuttassa bhikkhuno oḷārikā "
"upakkilesā kāyaduccaritaṃ vacīduccaritaṃ manoduccaritaṃ, tamenaṃ sacetaso "
"bhikkhu dabbajātiko pajahati vinodeti byantīkaroti anabhāvaṃ gameti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.101:2.2"
msgid ""
"Tasmiṃ pahīne tasmiṃ byantīkate santi adhicittamanuyuttassa bhikkhuno "
"majjhimasahagatā upakkilesā kāmavitakko byāpādavitakko vihiṃsāvitakko, "
"tamenaṃ sacetaso bhikkhu dabbajātiko pajahati vinodeti byantīkaroti "
"anabhāvaṃ gameti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.101:2.3"
msgid ""
"Tasmiṃ pahīne tasmiṃ byantīkate santi adhicittamanuyuttassa bhikkhuno "
"sukhumasahagatā upakkilesā ñātivitakko janapadavitakko "
"anavaññattipaṭisaṃyutto vitakko, tamenaṃ sacetaso bhikkhu dabbajātiko "
"pajahati vinodeti byantīkaroti anabhāvaṃ gameti."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: dhammavitakkāvasissanti → dhammavitakkovasissati (mr)
msgctxt "an3.101:2.4"
msgid "Tasmiṃ pahīne tasmiṃ byantīkate athāparaṃ dhammavitakkāvasissanti."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: sasaṅkhāraniggayhavāritagato → sasaṅkhāraniggayhavāritavato (bj, s1-3, km, pts1) | sasaṅkhāraniggayhavārivāvato (mr) | sasaṅkhāraniggayhavāriyādhigato (?)
msgctxt "an3.101:2.5"
msgid ""
"So hoti samādhi na ceva santo na ca paṇīto nappaṭippassaddhaladdho na "
"ekodibhāvādhigato sasaṅkhāraniggayhavāritagato."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: sannisīdati ekodi hoti → ekodibhāvaṃ gacchati (si) | ekodibhāvo hoti (s1-3, km, mr)
msgctxt "an3.101:2.6"
msgid ""
"Hoti so, bhikkhave, samayo yaṃ taṃ cittaṃ ajjhattaṃyeva santiṭṭhati "
"sannisīdati ekodi hoti samādhiyati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.101:2.7"
msgid ""
"So hoti samādhi santo paṇīto paṭippassaddhiladdho ekodibhāvādhigato na "
"sasaṅkhāraniggayhavāritagato."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.101:2.8"
msgid ""
"Yassa yassa ca abhiññā sacchikaraṇīyassa dhammassa cittaṃ abhininnāmeti "
"abhiññā sacchikiriyāya tatra tatreva sakkhibhabbataṃ pāpuṇāti sati "
"satiāyatane."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
#. VAR: abhijjamāne → abhijjamāno (pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an3.101:3.1"
msgid ""
"So sace ākaṅkhati: ‘anekavihitaṃ iddhividhaṃ paccanubhaveyyaṃ—ekopi hutvā "
"bahudhā assaṃ, bahudhāpi hutvā eko assaṃ; āvibhāvaṃ, tirobhāvaṃ; tirokuṭṭaṃ "
"tiropākāraṃ tiropabbataṃ asajjamāno gaccheyyaṃ, seyyathāpi ākāse; "
"pathaviyāpi ummujjanimujjaṃ kareyyaṃ, seyyathāpi udake; udakepi abhijjamāne "
"gaccheyyaṃ, seyyathāpi pathaviyaṃ; ākāsepi pallaṅkena kameyyaṃ, seyyathāpi "
"pakkhī sakuṇo; imepi candimasūriye evaṃmahiddhike evaṃmahānubhāve pāṇinā "
"parimaseyyaṃ parimajjeyyaṃ; yāva brahmalokāpi kāyena vasaṃ vatteyyan’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.101:3.2"
msgid "tatra tatreva sakkhibhabbataṃ pāpuṇāti sati satiāyatane."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an3.101:4.1"
msgid ""
"So sace ākaṅkhati: ‘dibbāya sotadhātuyā visuddhāya atikkantamānusikāya ubho "
"sadde suṇeyyaṃ dibbe ca mānuse ca ye dūre santike cā’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.101:4.2"
msgid "tatra tatreva sakkhibhabbataṃ pāpuṇāti sati satiāyatane."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an3.101:5.1"
msgid ""
"So sace ākaṅkhati: ‘parasattānaṃ parapuggalānaṃ cetasā ceto paricca "
"pajāneyyaṃ—sarāgaṃ vā cittaṃ sarāgaṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ, vītarāgaṃ vā "
"cittaṃ vītarāgaṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ; sadosaṃ vā cittaṃ sadosaṃ cittanti "
"pajāneyyaṃ, vītadosaṃ vā cittaṃ vītadosaṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ; samohaṃ vā "
"cittaṃ samohaṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ, vītamohaṃ vā cittaṃ vītamohaṃ cittanti "
"pajāneyyaṃ; saṅkhittaṃ vā cittaṃ saṅkhittaṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ, vikkhittaṃ "
"vā cittaṃ vikkhittaṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ; mahaggataṃ vā cittaṃ mahaggataṃ "
"cittanti pajāneyyaṃ, amahaggataṃ vā cittaṃ amahaggataṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ; "
"sauttaraṃ vā cittaṃ sauttaraṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ, anuttaraṃ vā cittaṃ "
"anuttaraṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ; samāhitaṃ vā cittaṃ samāhitaṃ cittanti "
"pajāneyyaṃ, asamāhitaṃ vā cittaṃ asamāhitaṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ; vimuttaṃ vā "
"cittaṃ vimuttaṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ, avimuttaṃ vā cittaṃ avimuttaṃ cittanti "
"pajāneyyan’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.101:5.2"
msgid "tatra tatreva sakkhibhabbataṃ pāpuṇāti sati satiāyatane."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.256"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an3.101:6.1"
msgid ""
"So sace ākaṅkhati: ‘anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussareyyaṃ, seyyathidaṃ—"
"ekampi jātiṃ dvepi jātiyo tissopi jātiyo catassopi jātiyo pañcapi jātiyo "
"dasapi jātiyo vīsampi jātiyo tiṃsampi jātiyo cattālīsampi jātiyo paññāsampi "
"jātiyo jātisatampi jātisahassampi jātisatasahassampi anekepi saṃvaṭṭakappe "
"anekepi vivaṭṭakappe anekepi saṃvaṭṭavivaṭṭakappe: “amutrāsiṃ evaṃnāmo "
"evaṅgotto evaṃvaṇṇo evamāhāro evaṃsukhadukkhappaṭisaṃvedī evamāyupariyanto, "
"so tato cuto amutra udapādiṃ; tatrāpāsiṃ evaṃnāmo evaṅgotto evaṃvaṇṇo "
"evamāhāro evaṃsukhadukkhappaṭisaṃvedī evamāyupariyanto, so tato cuto "
"idhūpapanno”ti, iti sākāraṃ sauddesaṃ anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussareyyan’"
"ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.101:6.2"
msgid "tatra tatreva sakkhibhabbataṃ pāpuṇāti sati satiāyatane."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an3.101:7.1"
msgid ""
"So sace ākaṅkhati: ‘dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena satte "
"passeyyaṃ cavamāne upapajjamāne hīne paṇīte suvaṇṇe dubbaṇṇe, sugate duggate "
"yathākammūpage satte pajāneyyaṃ: “ime vata bhonto sattā kāyaduccaritena "
"samannāgatā vacīduccaritena samannāgatā manoduccaritena samannāgatā ariyānaṃ "
"upavādakā micchādiṭṭhikā micchādiṭṭhikammasamādānā, te kāyassa bhedā paraṃ "
"maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapannā; ime vā pana bhonto sattā "
"kāyasucaritena samannāgatā vacīsucaritena samannāgatā manosucaritena "
"samannāgatā ariyānaṃ anupavādakā sammādiṭṭhikā sammādiṭṭhikammasamādānā, te "
"kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapannā”ti, iti dibbena "
"cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena satte passeyyaṃ cavamāne "
"upapajjamāne hīne paṇīte suvaṇṇe dubbaṇṇe, sugate duggate yathākammūpage "
"satte pajāneyyan’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.101:7.2"
msgid "tatra tatreva sakkhibhabbataṃ pāpuṇāti sati satiāyatane."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an3.101:8.1"
msgid ""
"So sace ākaṅkhati: ‘āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ "
"diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja vihareyyan’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.101:8.2"
msgid "tatra tatreva sakkhibhabbataṃ pāpuṇāti sati satiāyatane”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.101:8.3"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""
